data.description: **Motivated seller!      Welcome to 1706 E. Beverly, nestled within the beautiful Oaklawn neighborhood! This traditional style home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1904 sqft of living space. It boasts an open concept living room with eat-in kitchen, and separate formal dining room perfect for entertaining with the upcoming holidays! The storage space in this home is phenomenal! With the two car garage and extended driveway space, you can rest assured knowing your vehicles are safe and secure. With a large fenced-in backyard, you will have plenty of space to throw a terrific get-together. Additionally, this gem is conveniently located with amazing amenities like a 5-minute walk to the elementary school and community park!
